{"data":[{"name":"102:1","price":"तुम्हें (धन, संतान की) बहुतायत पर गर्व ने ग़ाफ़िल कर दिया।","arabic":"أَلۡهَىٰكُمُ ٱلتَّكَاثُرُ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6169,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"alhākumu al-takāthuru ","translations":["Diverts you","the competition to increase","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["alhākumu","al-takāthuru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1350],[2,1350,3315]]}},{"name":"102:2","price":"यहाँ तक कि तुम क़ब्रिस्तान जा पहुँचे।[1]","arabic":"حَتَّىٰ زُرۡتُمُ ٱلۡمَقَابِرَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6170,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1. (1-2) इन दोनों आयतों में उनको सावधान किया गया है, जो सांसारिक धन ही को सब कुछ समझते हैं और उसे अधिकाधिक प्राप्त करने की धुन उनपर ऐसी सवार है कि मौत के पार क्या होगा, इसे सोचते ही नहीं। कुछ तो धन की देवी बनाकर उसे पूजते हैं।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"ḥattā zur'tumu al-maqābira ","translations":["Until","you visit","the graves","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["ḥattā","zur'tumu","al-maqābira",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,930],[2,930,1800],[3,1800,3955]]}},{"name":"102:3","price":"कदापि नहीं, तुम शीघ्र ही जान लोगे।","arabic":"كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6171,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā sawfa taʿlamūna ","translations":["Nay","Soon","you will know","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","sawfa","taʿlamūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1570],[3,1570,5275]]}},{"name":"102:4","price":"फिर कदापि नहीं, तुम शीघ्र ही जान लोगे।","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6172,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma kallā sawfa taʿlamūna ","translations":["Then","nay","Soon","you will know","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","kallā","sawfa","taʿlamūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1620],[2,1620,2530],[3,2530,3320],[4,3320,6665]]}},{"name":"102:5","price":"कदापि नहीं, यदि तुम निश्चित ज्ञान के साथ जान लेते (तो ऐसा न करते)।[2]","arabic":"كَلَّا لَوۡ تَعۡلَمُونَ عِلۡمَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6173,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"2. (3-5) इन आयतों में सावधान किया गया है कि मौत के पार क्या है? उन्हें आँख बंद करते ही इसका ज्ञान हो जाएगा। यदि आज तुम्हें इस का विश्वास होता, तो अपने भविष्य की ओर से निश्चिन्त न होते। और तुम पर धन प्राप्ति की धुन इतनी सवार न होती।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā law taʿlamūna ʿil'ma al-yaqīni ","translations":["Nay","If","you know","(with) a knowledge","(of) certainty","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","law","taʿlamūna","ʿil'ma","al-yaqīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,960],[2,960,1270],[3,1270,2520],[4,2520,3140],[5,3140,6505]]}},{"name":"102:6","price":"निश्चय तुम अवश्य जहन्नम को देखोगे।","arabic":"لَتَرَوُنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6174,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"latarawunna al-jaḥīma ","translations":["Surely you will see","the Hellfire","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["latarawunna","al-jaḥīma",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2230],[2,2230,5995]]}},{"name":"102:7","price":"फिर निश्चय तुम उसे अवश्य विश्वास की आँख से देखोगे।","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَتَرَوُنَّهَا عَيۡنَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6175,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma latarawunnahā ʿayna al-yaqīni ","translations":["Then","surely you will see it","(with the) eye","(of) certainty","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","latarawunnahā","ʿayna","al-yaqīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1100],[2,1100,3870],[3,3870,4450],[4,4450,7995]]}},{"name":"102:8","price":"फिर निश्चय तुम उस दिन नेमतों के बारे में अवश्य पूछे जाओगे।[3]","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَتُسۡـَٔلُنَّ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَنِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6176,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"3. (6-8) इन आयतों में सूचित किया गया है कि तुम नरक के होने का विश्वास करो या न करो, वह दिन आकर रहेगा जब तुम उसको अपनी आँखों से देख लोगे। उस समय तुम्हें इसका पूरा विश्वास हो जाएगा। परंतु वह दिन कर्म का नहीं ह़िसाब देने का दिन होगा। और तुम्हें प्रत्येक अनुकंपा (नेमत) के बारे में अल्लाह के सामने जवाबदेही करनी होगी। (अह़्सनुल बयान)","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma latus'alunna yawma-idhin ʿani al-naʿīmi ","translations":["Then","surely you will be asked","that Day","about","the pleasures","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","latus'alunna","yawma-idhin","ʿani","al-naʿīmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1580],[2,1580,3839],[3,3839,5159],[4,5159,5639],[5,5639,11874]]}}],"chapter":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur","Chapter At-Takathur","Takathur","Surah Takathur","Chapter Takathur","At Takathur","Surah At Takathur","Chapter At Takathur","Surah 102","Chapter 102","The Rivalry","التكاثر"],"version":{"key":"hindi_omari","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"hi","version":"1.1.4","last_update":1675069101,"title":"Hindi Translation","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Indian by Azizul-Haqq Al-Umary."}}